{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21243.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":101301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":300401,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":300401,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Sasara","textRight":"Well, special influence or not, we need@the site to gain more popularity now.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":101301,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"You're right! It's unfortunate about Sayuki-senpai,"},{"chara":[{"id":101301}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"but there must still be a way to spread@the word about the petition!"},{"nameNarration":"Meiyui","narration":"Then I have a good idea.","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":130.0},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301201,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Meiyui","narration":"This is something I heard from a@Blue Seas Family associate,","narrationBg":"","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":130.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"but social media services have@a function called \"hashtag\", yes?"},{"chara":[{"id":301201,"motion":200}],"narration":"We will use that."},{"chara":[{"id":301201}],"narration":"If you place a \"#\" symbol@before a word that is a \"trend\"@on a post you wish to spread,"},{"chara":[{"id":301201,"motion":100}],"narration":"then everyone may see it."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_14033.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301201,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":302301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":302301,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"Hmm, I'm pretty sure I've seen@a phrase that was trending, too.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":302301}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"What topic was it though?@Something I searched a bunch."},{"chara":[{"id":302301}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"Must've been something that would catch@the eye of young people like me..."},{"chara":[{"id":302301,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"Is it..."},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"Please sign from the link below!@www.～～～～@#FinishDecagonBallUniverse","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":130.0},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":302301,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Aimi","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"...Something like that?"},{"chara":[{"id":301201,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Meiyui","textLeft":"That is it, much like that! Very good sense!"},{"chara":[{"id":302301,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"Well, chances are it will get@more eyes on the petition,"},{"chara":[{"id":302301}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"but like, I wonder if unrelated people@will start seeing the site..."},{"chara":[{"id":302301,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"And...the way we're doing it...like...they'd think@we're sending them to a scam site..."},{"chara":[{"id":302301}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"I think we'll get some disapproval from them..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":301201,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Meiyui","textLeft":"[chara:301201:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]What―?!"},{"chara":[{"id":301201}],"nameLeft":"Meiyui","textLeft":"The Blue Seas Family would never scam, we are@a wholesome, clean organization!!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":302301,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"Y-yeah... I know that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":302301,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Aimi","textRight":"But like, hashtags are more"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":302301,"motion":100}],"nameNarration":"Aimi","narration":"\"[textRed:I want my words to reach out@to tons of people.]\"","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":302301}],"nameRight":"Aimi","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"That's basically what they're for, don't you think...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":301201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Meiyui","textLeft":"Romanticist, are we."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_18023.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":303601,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":304201,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":303601,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Maria","textLeft":"But even with varying opinions,","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":303601}],"nameLeft":"Maria","textLeft":"I don't think the idea itself to use trends is bad."},{"chara":[{"id":303601,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Maria","textLeft":"If a trend that's especially relevant@to the petition gets popular,"},{"chara":[{"id":303601}],"nameLeft":"Maria","textLeft":"then far from disapproving of it, it may@make people want to sign it themselves."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":304201,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Meguru","textRight":"So current trends are..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":304201,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Meguru","textRight":"Hmm, there isn't anything really related to it,@is there."},{"chara":[{"id":304201}],"nameRight":"Meguru","textRight":"And setting the region to \"Kamihama\" to narrow it@down..."},{"chara":[{"id":304201,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Meguru","textRight":"It's just filled with hunger and thirst..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":303601,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Maria","textLeft":"You're right..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21243.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":101301,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":300401,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":101301}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"Any other good ideas...?","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":300401,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Sasara","textRight":"Is there no other way...?"},{"bgm":"stop","nameNarration":"","narration":"~~♪~~♪","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","surround":"7105_telphone"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":300601,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Emiri","narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"[chara:300601:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":300601,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Emiri","textRight":"Group call! It's from RuiRui―!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":305601,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story10","chara":[{"id":305601,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Rui","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"G-GUUUYS―!","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":305601}],"nameCenter":"Rui","textCenter":"U-umm... A-anyway, there's trouble―!"},{"chara":[{"id":305601,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Rui","textCenter":"E-everyone get over here now―!"},{"chara":[{"id":305601,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Rui","textCenter":"I'm between Kosho Ward and Daito Ward."},{"chara":[{"id":305601}],"nameCenter":"Rui","textCenter":"By a huge river, though...@I-I'll post a map in a second..."},{"chara":[{"id":305601,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Rui","textCenter":"For some reason there's c-crowds of people here."},{"chara":[{"id":305601}],"nameCenter":"Rui","textCenter":"Anyway, this is going to get really bad...!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21243.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":101301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":300601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":101301,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"I don't know what is happening,@but she said it's trouble.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":300601}],"nameRight":"Emiri","textRight":"It's rare for RuiRui to call on the phone."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":300401,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Sasara","textLeft":"It's a little far, though, so let's get moving!"},{"chara":[{"id":300601,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Emiri","textRight":"Right, the trains have stopped~"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":101301,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Asuka","textLeft":"To the rooftops at once!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
